- `gopls`
- `goimports`
- `golangci-lint`
- `gotestsum`
- `govulncheck`
- `dlv` (Delve debugger)

<if HAS_GOLANGCI_CONFIG>
Host `~/.golangci.yml` / `~/.golangci.yaml` was copied to `/home/sandbox/`.
</if>

### Building

Build binaries to the project `bin/` directory:

```bash
go build -o ./bin/ ./...
```

All compiled binaries are Linux arm64 — they will not run on macOS.

### Recommended workflow

```bash
goimports -w .
golangci-lint run ./...
gotestsum -- -race ./...
govulncheck ./...
```

